import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Socket } from 'ngx-socket-io'; import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; @Component({ selector: 'app-root', templateUrl: './app.component.html', styleUrls: ['./app.component.css'] }) export class AppComponent { data: Array<{offerId: string, status: string}> = []; title = 'webangular'; constructor(private http: HttpClient, private socket: Socket) { }; ngOnInit() { this.http.get('http://localhost:8080/amq').subscribe((data: any): void => { this.data = data.slice(0, 10); console.log('data from http : ' + data) }); this.socket.on('topico', (data: Array<{offerId: string, status: string}>) => { console.log(data); this.data = data; }); this.socket.emit('subscribe', { topic: 'topico' }); } }
